title: Molecular Structure
description: A 3D representation of a molecular structure, showcasing interconnected atoms arranged in a hexagonal lattice pattern. The atoms are depicted as spheres, connected by lines to represent chemical bonds, creating a visually appealing and scientific illustration.

title: Pink Crystals
description: A collection of rough pink crystals, showcasing various shades of pink and purple. The crystals have a translucent quality and are irregularly shaped, reflecting light in different ways.

title: Spiral Shell
description: A close-up view of a spiral shell with a smooth, glossy surface. The shell features a gradient of warm colors, including shades of orange, cream, and light brown, arranged in concentric circles that enhance its spiral shape.

title: Amber Glass Bottle
description: An amber glass bottle with a narrow neck and a black cap. The bottle has a smooth surface and is typically used for storing liquids, protecting contents from light.

title: Green Tourmaline Crystal
description: A green tourmaline crystal, characterized by its elongated, prismatic shape and vibrant green color. The crystal has a slightly rough surface and is cut at an angle, revealing its internal structure.

title: Brass Cube on Rock
description: The image features a small brass cube resting on a rough, natural rock surface. The cube has a flat top with a small protrusion, and the rock appears to be irregularly shaped, showcasing its natural texture and color.
